title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Jun 14 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Jun 14 2022
description:
Buck hosts the final hour solo, with Clay leaving for NYC. The Clay Travis & Buck Sexton Show one-year anniversary celebration is later this week in NYC. Crime wave Democrats unleashed spreads to rural America. Suspect being chased by Seattle police calls 911, cites law against illegal pursuit. Andrew Giuliani joins Buck to talk about his run for NY governor. Buck takes calls to close out the show.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
